{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Create a modern, clean Shopify homepage inspired by Tentree.com. Use a minimalist nature-style layout, large lifestyle banners, rounded cards, soft shadows, white space, smooth fade/slide animations, and subtle slow-scroll background movement (light parallax motion).
    
    === HERO SECTION ===
    • Full-width hero banner (soft parallax background).
    • Single H1: “Premium Wall Art & Professional UV Printing Services”
    • Subheading: “Shop premium wall art or book fast, same-day UV printing services.”
    • Two CTA buttons:
       - Shop By Category → #wall-art
       - Book Services → #services
    • Centered layout like Tentree hero.
    
    === SILO 1 — WALL ART (PRODUCTS) ===
    Add H2 with ID="wall-art": “Paintings & Posters by Category”.
    Below it create a clean 4-card grid (Tentree category block style):
    Each card must include:
      • Small parallax banner image
      • Rounded corners and soft shadows
      • H3 title linking to collections:
          - Canvas Paintings → /collections/canvas-paintings
          - Metal Posters → /collections/metal-posters
          - Acrylic Posters → /collections/acrylic-posters
          - UV Printed Frames → /collections/uv-printed-frames
      • 15–20 word description
      • Button: “Explore Collection”
      • Fade-in or slide-up animation
    
    === SILO 2 — PRINTING SERVICES ===
    Add H2 with ID="services": “Printing Services by Category”.
    Create a matching 4-card Tentree-style service grid:
    Each card includes:
      • Subtle parallax background
      • Rounded card layout
      • H3 title linking to service collections:
          - UV Flatbed Printing → /collections/uv-flatbed-printing
          - Eco-Solvent Printing → /collections/eco-solvent-printing
          - Latex Printing → /collections/latex-printing
          - Signage Printing → /collections/signage-printing
      • 15–20 word description
      • Button: “View Service”
      • Fade/slide animation
    
    === SEO + HEADING RULES ===
    • Only 1 H1 on entire page (in hero).
    • Use H2 only for the 2 silos.
    • Use H3 for category/service cards.
    • No H4 on homepage.
    
{% enddoc %}
